    slug: `sunnova-bankruptcy-what-homeowners-can-do`,
    title: `Sunnova Bankruptcy: What This Means for Your Solar Loan and Lease`,
    metaTitle: `Sunnova Bankruptcy: How Homeowners Can Cancel Solar Contract`,
    metaDescription: `Sunnova filed for bankruptcy--what does this mean for your solar loan or lease? Learn how to cancel your Sunnova contract and protect your home from solar fraud.`,
